      </processinfo>
      <relatedmaterial id="aspace_451a5740315302900cc6236e6463dd11">
         <head>Related Materials</head>
         <p>In the Periodicals collections, see: Aegis - Magazine on Ending Violence Against Women (formerly Feminist Alliance Against Rape Newsletter).</p>
         <p>See also the Loretta Ross papers.</p>  
      </relatedmaterial>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_8967b736fb5e6802ce044d95975ef68e">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>Includes information on marches sponsored by the Center, the contents of an orientation packet, various pamphlets and publications by the Center, four issues of <title>Black Belt Woman</title> magazine, photocopied articles, and a workbook for children.</p>
         <p>Additions to the collection include handwritten notes (loose and in notebooks), largely by Deb Friedman, on FAAR meeting proceedings, as well as notes on Aegis newsletters, agendas, and member phone/mailing lists, all of which reflect the work of these groundbreaking efforts to address issues around violence against women.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
